duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide quality calls and represent the dealership in a positive and professional manner.
Effectively communicate using proper English, grammar, and professional etiquette.
Navigate dual screen, multi-tab, multiple platform programs while guiding a phone conversation with a prospect.
Take notes during the call of the relevant points for the dealership.
Effective and professional communication in a one-on-one and team environment.
Effectively manage time and multitasking ability.
